果啲<br />\n做吓kegel exercise train翻啲肌肉<br />\n同埋去廁所果陣屙完一次<br />\n等一陣<br />\n試吓睇吓屙唔屙到第二次<br />\n屙清佢<br />\n記得睇醫生"},{"pid":"736177f8a5468d5c3b5f60531bb3c7488a15d368","tid":936182,"uid":62471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1254d37022c297127d25f2e974cf8cf511bfaa7b","tid":936182,"uid":191405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080b53dd5011dd631fe7509d3bc6c0f30dd84184","tid":936182,"uid":92071,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我之前又係返工返到咁，去完廁所唔夠半個鐘就急，搭巴士搭到一半要落車去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生發現係尿道炎，即刻有理無理，兩三個鐘就去一次廁所先，啲人話飲紅莓汁都有用～唔知係心理作用定咩係好咗少少，同埋成日凝住自己想去就會越諗越急 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"紅莓汁！抄低先 試下有無用！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T19:14:59.000Z","msg":"紅莓汁係用黎舒緩尿道炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1ecac701b1b2e03821c17d573799e2a93bddb0","tid":936182,"uid":175108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1254d37022c297127d25f2e974cf8cf511bfaa7b","tid":936182,"uid":191405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080b53dd5011dd631fe7509d3bc6c0f30dd84184","tid":936182,"uid":92071,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我之前又係返工返到咁，去完廁所唔夠半個鐘就急，搭巴士搭到一半要落車去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生發現係尿道炎，即刻有理無理，兩三個鐘就去一次廁所先，啲人話飲紅莓汁都有用～唔知係心理作用定咩係好咗少少，同埋成日凝住自己想去就會越諗越急 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"紅莓汁！抄低先 試下有無用！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T19:18:33.000Z","msg":"唔好試健康食品啦<br />\n直接睇醫生啦<br />\n上左前列腺就好長手尾"},{"pid":"0c78597b979fb3690b914d9924753ccea369016e","tid":936182,"uid":143400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T22:15:46.000Z","msg":"1/10啦 你吹到咁撚柒好難信"},{"pid":"59f71c3631aceef42b49b3b10cd4644188b50794","tid":936182,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616f3bf665119fd6fd1849a2ee44e70d9e9ee9cc","tid":936182,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:30:43.000Z","msg":"睇到好急"},{"pid":"4012231b137af936b52d88bd8f3f043daecd8f49","tid":936182,"uid":187072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:48:57.000Z","msg":"絲?"},{"pid":"ccca2def06f686e286d6710dd84d7af8117947a5","tid":936182,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e01aafaa63f86f4dca511c97931715ef22849a1","tid":936182,"uid":191405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"小弟前排開始返工 <br />\n未摸熟啲嘢就迎來咗peak season<br />\n日日都忙到唔敢去廁所<br />\n次次都係急到漏先衝去廁所解決<br />\n哩兩個星期開始發現唔對路<br />\n<br />\n話說有日做做下野既時候<br />\n屌   下面濕濕地既<br />\n唔係倒瀉水無為意坐左落去咁on9掛<br />\n咁咁啱又feel到強烈尿意<br />\n就順便去廁所整理下<br />\n<br />\n一除褲 仆你個街   底褲濕咗成墶<br />\n好彩側邊無人 唔係實比人笑到面黃<br />\n唯有急急腳入廁格印走啲水漬<br />\n以為平安無事   返埋位<br />\n<br />\n坐低無幾耐就黎料啦   <br />\n陣騷臭既尿味   由我個位散發出去<br />\n啲同事都忍唔住問邊個踩尿<br />\n心知不妙既我唯有扮去影印 忍痛揼咗條底底佢<br />\n<br />\n自從嗰日起 我滲尿漏尿既情況愈黎愈頻密<br />\n到而家都係無改善<br />\n只係可以每隔三十分鐘提自己去一去廁所<br />\n<br />\n我而家先二十三歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:49:38.000Z","msg":"認真 下次急尿咇小小出黎就唔急嫁啦"},{"pid":"297c8112560739a6abcf5739fb0f0bf6951b9528","tid":936182,"uid":121291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"似係尿道炎"},{"pid":"336d914da2ddd7b2c2635732b703f76a4ee24396","tid":936182,"uid":45545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T01:22:55.000Z","msg":"Auditor?"},{"pid":"b852ade4ced644bc659fbe7f8a2442b57f57dc1e","tid":936182,"uid":214883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1254d37022c297127d25f2e974cf8cf511bfaa7b","tid":936182,"uid":191405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080b53dd5011dd631fe7509d3bc6c0f30dd84184","tid":936182,"uid":92071,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我之前又係返工返到咁，去完廁所唔夠半個鐘就急，搭巴士搭到一半要落車去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生發現係尿道炎，即刻有理無理，兩三個鐘就去一次廁所先，啲人話飲紅莓汁都有用～唔知係心理作用定咩係好咗少少，同埋成日凝住自己想去就會越諗越急 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"紅莓汁！抄低先 試下有無用！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"飲蛇舌草好似都會幫助尿道炎<br />\n但我覺得你要去睇醫生, 可能係膀胱炎/膀胱過度活躍症<br />\n如果係炎症嘅可以試下去藥房買日本草本配方嘅尿道/膀胱炎藥<br />\n試過幾有效"},{"pid":"50a00ade1806f8738433a3b3bc1060b635330601","tid":936182,"uid":196625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"我唔明有D 咩假膠唔假膠, 香港大撚把人工作至上到, 做到自己病到冇得返轉頭都唔知<br />\n<br />\n快撚D 去睇醫生, 考慮下辭職休息啦"},{"pid":"bc558750d27299f96998d6266c03d0b490a9d4ab","tid":936182,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"吸毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186c37730792df78acfb934b3ed4bd18cd4193bf","tid":936182,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"白痴<br />\n尿道炎睇醫生食抗生素啦<br />\n你再唔睇醫生屙血尿啦"},{"pid":"b3314212087056413ba8186edb59ce48eeddf1d7","tid":936182,"uid":24210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}